Develop a centralized web-based Travel Budget Allocation and Expense Tracking System that integrates budget allocation, travel requests, expense submission, and approval workflows into a single platform. The system provides real-time budget tracking, automatic budget deductions upon expense submission, configurable 50% and 80% threshold alerts, role-based dashboards, and comprehensive audit trails. This enables organizations to improve budget visibility, strengthen financial control, support proactive decision-making, and ensure compliance across all departments.